# workflow-requirement-clarify

Use this when a request is broad, ambiguous, or likely to affect contracts.

1. Restate the business outcome.
2. Ask which main flow and legacy flow are in scope.
3. Ask whether API/status/schema/frontend contracts may change.
4. Ask what verification is required.
5. Ask which human review areas apply: {{inlineList risks.humanReviewRequired}}.
6. Produce a concise requirement summary before planning or coding.
